{
  "stem": "10905.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was almost impossible to come to the United States then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, the-- the quota for Hungarian or Yugoslav Jews were almost nil, and it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my dad decided that he had had his fill of Europe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he could not get, obviously, a-- a piece of paper from the British that we could go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I assume you-- you know that, that  it was such terrific restriction on Jewish immigration to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So didn't want to remain a displaced person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did not want to go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're ready come to the New World, and you couldn't come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, they were very desperate for physicians in Bolivia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were going to go to Bolivia and start learning Spanish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About a month before we were supposed to go to Bolivia, we get an affidavit that, based upon a preference quota for physicians, we could come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So now shift gears.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have to now learn English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my father had to learn English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my sister and I took a few lessons in English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember the first thing I learned in English was about Beatrix Potter tales.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In 1947, in June, we left Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We traveled to Paris, and we spent a few days in Paris with-- and we stayed as a guest of Mr.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Havas, the one was in the film business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we went to London and stayed with one of my father's classmates from school, who was a dentist and was living in the West End.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
